title: Kristopher Woods, Two Bedroom Townhome
posting_body: ['Looking for a new home?', 'Come discover Kristopher Woods.', 'Diverse 214 units community 1, 2 and 3 bedroom Townhomes and Garden levels.', '1 and 2 story living.', 'Washer/Dryer connections with laundry room on site.', 'Tucked away in a lush tranquil setting of well-maintained grounds, our large one, two and three bedroom apartment homes are just minutes away from I-285, excellent schools, Stone Mountain Park and Northlake.', 'Please call our friendly staff today and receive more information!', 'Two Bedroom Townhome - $1195.00 (Available after October 14th, 2022)', '• Water, Trash, and Pest Control included in total.', 'Resident is responsible for activating power in their unit upon approval.', 'Prerequisites:', '• Income 3x the rent or more.', '• No Evictions, Collections, Felonies, or Bankruptcies on the background and credit check.', '• Credit Score Minimum of 550 or higher.', 'Application Process: Please call for more information.', 'Ask for Karla/Merima:', 'show contact info', '*Kristopher Woods Apartments*', '792 Jolly Avenue South', 'Clarkston, GA 30021', 'Monday-Friday between 9am to 5pm', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change at anytime*', '<URL>']
